
    <html xmlns:o="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" 
          xmlns:w="urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word" 
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40">
    <head>
        <title>Ideation Phase - Empathy Map Canvas</title>
        <style>
            body {
                font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', Arial, sans-serif;
                line-height: 1.6;
                color: #2d2724;
                background-color: #faf6eb;
                margin: 20px;
            }
            h1 {
                font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
                color: #c05c46;
                border-bottom: 2px solid #2d2724;
                padding-bottom: 5px;
            }
            h2, h3, h4 {
                font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
                color: #2d2724;
            }
            table {
                width: 100%;
                border-collapse: collapse;
                margin: 20px 0;
            }
            th, td {
                border: 2px solid #2d2724;
                padding: 10px;
                text-align: left;
            }
            th {
                background-color: #dda15e;
                color: #2d2724;
                font-weight: bold;
            }
            .meta-table {
                width: 50%;
                margin-bottom: 30px;
            }
            .meta-table th {
                background-color: #2d2724;
                color: #faf6eb;
            }
            .highlight {
                background-color: #faf6eb;
                font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
                padding: 2px 5px;
                border: 1px solid #2d2724;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <h1>Ideation Phase - Empathy Map Canvas</h1>
        <table class="meta-table">
            <tr><th>Parameter</th><th>Value</th></tr>
            <tr><td><b>Date</b></td><td>11 July 2026</td></tr>
            <tr><td><b>Team ID</b></td><td>TEAM-MERN-03</td></tr>
            <tr><td><b>Project Name</b></td><td>ShopEZ - Vintage Sepia Neubrutalist E-Commerce Platform</td></tr>
        </table>
        
    <h2>Target Customer: Vintage Tech & Gaming Collectible Enthusiasts</h2>
    <table>
        <tr>
            <th style="width: 50%;">THINK & FEEL</th>
            <th style="width: 50%;">HEAR</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                - "I want to shop on a site that feels as retro and cozy as the items I buy."<br>
                - "Is this checkout secure? Can I trust this retro-looking website?"<br>
                - "I love interactive designs and retro typewriter fonts!"
            </td>
            <td>
                - Friends talking about cool retro gaming pads and keyboards online.<br>
                - Communities recommending small boutique shops over Amazon.<br>
                - Reviews praising clean, interactive buyer layouts.
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>SAY & DO</th>
            <th>SEE</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                - Searches for "Ares Pro Controller" and "Vinyl Record Player".<br>
                - Completes checkout with the flipping credit card.<br>
                - Prints the invoice copy for a physical folder.
            </td>
            <td>
                - Sterile e-commerce designs everywhere else.<br>
                - Beautiful high-res product photos of items on ShopEZ.<br>
                - Responsive cards showing discount tags and remaining counts.
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <th>PAIN</th>
            <th>GAIN</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                - Frustration with boring corporate layouts.<br>
                - Stale user token errors that break checkout flows.
            </td>
            <td>
                - Nostalgic, pleasant shopping vibes.<br>
                - Secure credit card simulator logs.
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>
    
    </body>
    </html>
    